let rec eval (e,x,y) = match e with
| VarX -> 
x
| VarY -> 
y
| Sine e1 -> 
sin(pi *. eval (e1,x,y))
| Cosine e1 -> 
cos(pi *. eval (e1,x,y))
| Average (e1,e2) -> 
(eval (e1,x,y) +. eval (e2,x,y)) /. 2.0
| Times (e1,e2) -> 
eval (e1,x,y) *. eval (e2,x,y)
| Thresh (e1,e2,e3,e4) -> 
if (eval(e1,x,y)<eval(e2,x,y))
then eval(e3,x,y)
else eval(e4,x,y)
| ModF e1 ->
(match modf (eval (e1,x,y) *. 4.0) with
| (f, i) -> f
)
| SumOfSquares (e1,e2,e3) ->
((eval(e1,x,y) ** 2.0) 
+. (eval(e2,x,y) ** 2.0)
+. (eval(e3,x,y) ** 2.0)) /. 3.0

let rec assoc (d,k,l) = match l with
| [] -> d
| h::t -> match h with
| (ki,di) ->
if ki = k
then di
else assoc (d,k,t)
